        Lowest: 0.662
        Middle: 0.637
        Highest: 0.612

        Horizontal Positions for Peg 1:
        Tower 1: 0.12
        Tower 2: 0.49
        Tower 3: 0.915

        Horizontal Positions for Peg 2:
        Tower 1: 0.10
